-- Hezbollah Has `Real Possibility' of Taking Over Lebanon, Ashkenazi Says
-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 2010-11-16T09:35:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/hezbollah-has-real-possibility-of-taking-over-lebanon-ashkenazi-says.html
Israeli military chief Lieutenant
General Gabi Ashkenazi said that there is “a real possibility”
that the Shiite Muslim Hezbollah “will take over Lebanon.”
Ashkenazi made the comments in Canada yesterday and they were
posted on the Israel Defense Forces Web site today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gwen Ackerman in Jerusalem at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
